#: src-en/data/events_ships.xml.append:93
msgid ""
"data/events_ships.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RK_SCORCH_EXIT_BOSS\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Now that you've passed the test, the other gatekeepers allow you out of the "
"sector, and hint that since you even managed to leave the ship in one piece,"
" you may retrieve a special cruiser blueprint from the wreck!"
